reviewText: The cover shows a mustang but it has more Ford of Europe cars in it . Still interesting to watch.

Most of the footage here is of English Fords. The Consul, etc. There's very little footage of American Fords. I wouldn't mind if they had spent more time on the Zephyr and the Zodiac, but most of the footage is of the Consul. I'm giving it two stars because it's unusual. It's not very interesting.
